### =============================================================================
### Booking Service — http://localhost:3001
### =============================================================================
### Usage: Open in JetBrains IDE or VS Code (REST Client extension)
### Variables are defined in http-client.env.json
### =============================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@clientId = 019600cf-1000-7000-8000-000000000001
@vehicleId = 019600cf-2000-7000-8000-000000000002

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Health
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Create booking
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Create a booking (valid)
# @name createBooking
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "client_id": "{{clientId}}",
  "vehicle_id": "{{vehicleId}}",
  "scheduled_at": "2026-06-01T10:00:00Z",
  "pickup_address": "10 rue de Rivoli, 75001 Paris",
  "dropoff_address": "CDG Terminal 2E, 95700 Roissy-en-France",
  "total_amount": 4500,
  "estimated_distance": 32500,
  "co2_grams": 4200
}

### Create a booking — missing client_id (expect 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicle_id": "{{vehicleId}}",
  "scheduled_at": "2026-06-01T10:00:00Z",
  "pickup_address": "10 rue de Rivoli, 75001 Paris",
  "dropoff_address": "CDG Terminal 2E, 95700 Roissy-en-France"
}

### Create a booking — scheduled_at in the past (expect 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "client_id": "{{clientId}}",
  "vehicle_id": "{{vehicleId}}",
  "scheduled_at": "2020-01-01T10:00:00Z",
  "pickup_address": "10 rue de Rivoli, 75001 Paris",
  "dropoff_address": "CDG Terminal 2E, 95700 Roissy-en-France"
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Get booking
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Get booking by ID — replace with ID from createBooking response
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/REPLACE_WITH_BOOKING_ID

### Get booking — not found (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/019600cf-0000-7000-8000-000000000000

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### List bookings
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### List bookings by client
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings?client_id={{clientId}}

### List bookings — missing client_id (expect 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Lifecycle transitions
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Confirm booking — replace with real ID
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bookings/REPLACE_WITH_BOOKING_ID/confirm

### Complete booking — must be CONFIRMED first
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bookings/REPLACE_WITH_BOOKING_ID/complete

### Cancel booking
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bookings/REPLACE_WITH_BOOKING_ID/cancel

### Confirm already cancelled booking (expect 422 — invalid transition)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bookings/REPLACE_WITH_BOOKING_ID/confirm